This paper deals with the problem of semantic annotation of web content, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of schema.org vocabulary and domain specifications also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and database systems (cs.DB). Finally, the tourism domain is a specific application area that could be relevant to cybersecurity (cs.CY) due to potential privacy and security concerns related to personal information and online transactions.
